These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: fuchsia, pink
The people have 2 different jobs:  teacher, librarian
1. the teacher is on the far left##1
2. the librarian is not the person who likes pink##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | pink   | fuchsia  |
| Sport   | teacher | librarian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, brazilian
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, bartender
1. the chef is on the left of the bartender##1
2. the chef is not the brazilian##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | chinese | brazilian      |
| Pet    | chef  | bartender |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
The people use 2 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski
The people have 2 different hobbies: fishing, traveling
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is not the person driving the boat##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | jet-ski  | boat    |
| Sport   | fishing | traveling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
