 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-5::.
2 different pets are kept: turtle, ferret
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, red
1. the owner of the ferret is not the person who likes red##6
2. the owner of the ferret is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Movie-Genre   | turtle  | ferret |
| Sport         | red | ivory      |

 #################################

 
