.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-7::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower
City: liverpool, rome
1. the person who growsbegonia is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growsbegonia is not the person traveling to rome##6

.:: Answer ::.
|       |     1      |       2       |
| Job   | begonia | balloon-flower |
| Pet   | liverpool       | rome       |

